divs: Sighting DetailsI walked across Westminster Bridge goingtowards Big Ben when 3 bright balls apeeared above the House of Parliament to myleft. They were re-orange and moved very fast. In addition they twirled aroundeach other. They were VERY clear to see although it lasted only about 3 or 4seconds. I was calm but stunned that this appeared above the House of Parliamentin central London. The balls sped away over the building and simply disappeared.
